children.value: _selectLoader(loaders : Object | Object[] | null, url? : String, data? : ArrayBuffer | String, options? : Object)
Selects an appropriate loader for a file from a list of candidate loaders by examining a URL and/or an initial data chunk.
- can be a single loader or an array of loaders, or null.
- An optional URL to perform autodetection against.
- Optional data to perform autodetection against
- Return null instead of throwing exception if no loader can be found
